		<td class="smallfont"><b>Wow...if everyone else is being brave</b></td>
		<td class="smallfont" align="right" wrap="nowrap">Post #<b><a href="showpost.php?s=528a06a87a69a909210d1e53ce6f655f&amp;postid=96624&postcount=1" target="new">1</a></b></td>
